author: gstein
msg: Add a utility function to do all the work for fetching baseline-related
information. This function does the several PROPFINDs necessary to map from
a URL to its Baseline Collection (BC), to fetch the latest revision number,
and to get the BC-relative path for a resource.
* props.c (svn_ra_dav__get_baseline_info): new function. most of the
content is from fetch.c::begin_checkout. Added more stuff to deal with
(begin_checkout): slice out a ton of code, use get_baseline_info instead.
